OL,3,CThe Beat goes on ` Paul McCartney
OL,4,Creleases duet with Ringo Starr
OL,6,FSir Paul McCartney has released a duet
OL,7,Fwith his former Beatles bandmate Sir
OL,8,FRingo Starr.
OL,10,FThe song, Home To Us, was released on
OL,11,FFriday and is part of Sir Paul's
OL,12,Fforthcoming solo album.
OL,14,FThe track also features Chrissie Hynde
OL,15,Fand Sharleen Spiteri on backing vocals.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
