PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778324573
OL,3,CThe Beat goes on ` Paul McCartney
OL,4,Creleases duet with Ringo Starr
OL,6,FThe new album, titled The Boys Of
OL,7,FDungeon Lane, recounts a collection of
OL,8,Fmemories from the singer's formative
OL,9,Fyears in Liverpool, including his
OL,10,Fearly adventures with his late
OL,11,Fbandmates George Harrison and John
OL,12,FLennon, prior to their Beatles fame.
OL,14,FSir Paul named the introspective 14-
OL,15,Ftrack record after Dungeon Lane, a
OL,16,Fplace close to his childhood home in
OL,17,FForthlin Road in the Liverpool suburb
OL,18,Fof Speke.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
