OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778324573
OL,3,CThe Beat goes on ` Paul McCartney
OL,4,Creleases duet with Ringo Starr
OL,6,FThe album, his first in five years, is
OL,7,Fdue to be released on May 29, with Sir
OL,8,FPaul previously describing the
OL,9,Finspiration behind it as "a lot of
OL,10,Fmemories of Liverpool".
OL,12,F"We didn't have much at all but it
OL,13,Fdidn't matter because all the people
OL,14,Fwere great and you didn't notice you
OL,15,Fdidn't have much," he added.
OL,17,FThe record will also feature a number
OL,18,Fof new love songs and reflections from
OL,19,Fthe artist on his life before he found
OL,20,Fglobal fame.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@VO]tD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
