OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778324573
OL,3,CThe Beat goes on ` Paul McCartney
OL,4,Creleases duet with Ringo Starr
OL,6,FHe released lead single, Days We Left
OL,7,FBehind, in March.
OL,9,FSir Paul's new studio album was
OL,10,Fproduced by Andrew Watt and began
OL,11,Fnearly five years ago with the opening
OL,12,Ftrack, As You Lie There.
OL,14,FFormer Beatles drummer Sir Ringo
OL,15,Freleased his latest solo album last
OL,16,Fmonth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
