PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778324573
OL,3,CThe Beat goes on ` Paul McCartney
OL,4,Creleases duet with Ringo Starr
OL,6,FThe 10-track record, Long Long Road,
OL,7,Ffeatures collaborations with Billy
OL,8,FStrings, Sheryl Crow and St Vincent,
OL,9,Fand was co-written with American
OL,10,Fproducer T Bone Burnett.
OL,12,FIt followed on from Sir Ringo's 2025
OL,13,Falbum Look Up, which marked his first
OL,14,Fnumber one album on the UK's official
OL,15,Fcountry chart.
OL,17,FThe Beatles were formed in 1960,
OL,18,Fcomprising Sir Paul, Lennon, Harrison
OL,19,Fand Sir Ringo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
