PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1778324573
OL,3,CThe Beat goes on ` Paul McCartney
OL,4,Creleases duet with Ringo Starr
OL,6,FThe band became the best-selling
OL,7,Fmusical act of all time and one of the
OL,8,Fmost influential groups in the world,
OL,9,Fhaving achieved 16 UK number one
OL,10,Falbums and 18 UK number one singles
OL,11,Fincluding Help!, Hey Jude and She
OL,12,FLoves You.
OL,14,FFollowing their split in 1970, Sir
OL,15,FPaul released his debut solo album,
OL,16,FMcCartney.
OL,18,FHe also formed the band Wings with his
OL,19,Flate wife Linda McCartney along with
OL,20,Fformer Moody Blues guitarist Denny
OL,21,FLaine.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
