OL,3,CThe Beat goes on ` Paul McCartney
OL,4,Creleases duet with Ringo Starr
OL,6,FPrior to splitting in 1981, the band
OL,7,Frecorded seven studio albums including
OL,8,FBand On The Run and achieved 12 UK top
OL,9,F10 singles including Jet, Silly Love
OL,10,FSongs and Live And Let Die, the theme
OL,11,Fto the 1973 James Bond film.
